A LoRA for creating anal gape and creampie photos.

If you feel like supporting my work, please consider visiting my Patreon to get access to more detailed instructions on how to get the most out of my models and have a say in what's up next: Link.

Update:

I wasn't happy with how there was no control of the size of the gape, so I added trigger words for that in V4.

Use 'anal gape' as the general trigger word.

'Average', 'large' and 'massive' control the size of the gape, 'penis' adds a penis.

'From front' and 'from behind' control the pose.

Creampies come out too intense most of the time and reduce the size of the gape, so I recommend to reduce the strength of that trigger word, like (creampie:0.7) for example.

Recommended LoRA strength ~0.7

To get rid of the hands add 'hands' and 'fingers' etc. to your negative prompt.

Based on UberRealisticPornMerge

If you like this, you may also like my Doggystyle Anal + Crempie LoRA.
